Article-I.D.: news.1992Jul26.234433.18018
Sender: usenet@news.acns.nwu.edu (Usenet on news.acns)
Organization: Northwestern University, Evanston Illinois.
Lines: 651

Hi, everyone.

Here is the 2nd game in the Dang Hu series.

This one is dedicated to *panx*!  My "brother" on IGS :-)  Panx was clearly
the best among the kibitzers, and his commentating was so attractive that
we have missed him badly since he "disappeared" from IGS.  Yes, he will be
back, but sooner the better.

An interesting observation: panx' real name, Pan Xiao Feng, has initials of
pxf, while one of the two great players we introduce here, Fan Xi Ping, has
initials of fxp.  So, pxf and fxp. :-)

Where are you, brother?! 

jzy, NR ^_^


